  "keyFeatures": [
    "Automatic phone number formatting to E.164 international standard using the phonenumbers library",
    "WebRTC-based browser softphone widget integrated into Odoo's UI via SIP.js",
    "PBX server management with test and production environment modes",
    "Caller ID lookup — match incoming phone numbers to Odoo partners",
    "Call history tracking with states (calling, ongoing, missed, terminated, rejected)",
    "Click-to-dial from partner views and call activity scheduling",
    "Extensible phone model registry via _phone_name_sequence and _phone_name_fields",
    "Compatible with Zerovoz, Ringover, Axivox, and OnSIP VOIP providers"
  ],
